trans-unit.source: Provides a base implementation of a toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: Gir en base implementering av et verktøykassen-element.

trans-unit.source: ToolboxItem is a base class for toolbox items that can be displayed in the toolbox of a design-time environment.
trans-unit.target: ToolboxItem er en basisklasse for verktøykassen elementer som kan vises i verktøykassen i et miljø med utformingen.

trans-unit.source: A toolbox item typically represents a component to create when invoked on a design mode document.
trans-unit.target: Et element for verktøykassen representerer vanligvis en komponent for å opprette når den startes på et dokument for utforming-modus.

trans-unit.source: The ToolboxItem class provides the methods and properties needed to provide the toolbox with the display properties for the toolbox item, to create a component or components when used, and to serialize and deserialize itself for persistence within the toolbox database.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ToolboxItem gir metodene og egenskapene som kreves for å gi verktøykassen visningsegenskapene for verktøykasseelementet til å opprette en komponent eller komponenter når den brukes, og til å serialisere og deserialisere selve for utholdenhet i verktøykassen-databasen.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the ToolboxItem class can be configured with a name, bitmap, and type to create, without creating a class that derives from ToolboxItem.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av klassen ToolboxItem kan konfigureres med et navn, punktgrafikk og type for å opprette uten å opprette en klasse som er avledet fra ToolboxItem.

trans-unit.source: The ToolboxItem class also provides a base class for custom toolbox item implementations.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ToolboxItem tilbyr også en basisklasse for egendefinert verktøykassen elementet implementeringer.

trans-unit.source: A custom ToolboxItem can create multiple components.
trans-unit.target: En egendefinert ToolboxItem kan opprette flere komponenter.

trans-unit.source: To implement a custom toolbox item, you must derive from ToolboxItem and override the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Serialize%2A>, and <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Deserialize%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: For å implementere et egendefinert verktøykassen-element, må du være avledet fra ToolboxItem og overstyre den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Serialize%2A>, og <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Deserialize%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Deserialize%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Serialize%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: The following properties and methods must be configured for a ToolboxItem to function correctly: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.DisplayName%2A> property specifies the label for the toolbox item when displayed in a toolbox.
trans-unit.target: Følgende egenskaper og metoder må konfigureres for ToolboxItem skal fungere riktig: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.DisplayName%2A>egenskapen angir etiketten for verktøykasseelementet når vises i en verktøykassen.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.DisplayName%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.TypeName%2A> property specifies the fully qualified name of the type of the component that the item creates.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.TypeName%2A>Egenskapen angir fullstendige navnet på komponenttypen elementet oppretter.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.TypeName%2A>

trans-unit.source: If a derived class creates multiple components, the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.TypeName%2A> property may or may not be used, contingent on whether a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A> method override depends on the value of this property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den utledede klassen oppretter flere komponenter i <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.TypeName%2A>egenskapen kan eller ikke kan brukes, avhengige av om en <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>metoden override, avhengig av verdien for denne egenskapen.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.TypeName%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.AssemblyName%2A> property specifies the assembly that contains the type of a component that the item creates.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.AssemblyName%2A>Egenskapen angir samlingen som inneholder en komponenttypen elementet oppretter.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.AssemblyName%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Bitmap%2A> property optionally specifies a bitmap image to display next to the display name for the toolbox item in the toolbox.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Bitmap%2A>Egenskapen angir eventuelt punktgrafikk til å vise neste visningsnavnet for verktøykasseelementet i verktøykassen.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Bitmap%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Filter%2A> property optionally contains any <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemFilterAttribute> objects that determine whether the toolbox item can be used on a particular component.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Filter%2A>Egenskapen eventuelt inneholder <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemFilterAttribute>objekter som bestemmer om verktøykasseelementet kan brukes på en bestemt komponent.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemFilterAttribute> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Filter%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A> method returns the component instance or instances to insert where this tool is used.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>Metoden returnerer komponentforekomsten eller forekomstene for å sette inn der dette verktøyet brukes.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Serialize%2A> method saves the toolbox item to a specified <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Serialize%2A>Metoden lagrer verktøykasseelementet til en angitt <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Serialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Deserialize%2A> method configures the toolbox item from the state information contained in the specified <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Deserialize%2A>Metoden konfigurerer verktøykasseelementet fra statusinformasjon i den angitte <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Deserialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Initialize%2A> method configures the toolbox item to create the specified type of component, if the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A> method has not been overridden to behave differently.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Initialize%2A>Metoden konfigurerer verktøykassen-element for å opprette den angitte typen av komponenten, hvis den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>metoden er ikke overstyrt for virkemåten annerledes.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Locked%2A> property indicates whether the properties of the toolbox item can be changed.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Locked%2A>Egenskapen angir om egenskaper for verktøykasseelementet kan endres.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.Locked%2A>
